EXECUTOR SERVICE (extends Executor)\
\
- provides methods for submitting tasks and managing termination\
- Lifecycle\
	Running\
	Shutting Down		-	use shutdown() which is graceful or \
						shutdownNow() which will interrupt active threads/tasks and ignore and return queued threads/tasks\
	Terminated		-	isTerminated() tells if Executor is terminated\
\
Methods\
- awaitTermination(int number, TimeUnit)		-	returns true if all tasks are complete and false otherwise\
