CLASS HIERARCHY\
\
Executor\
	ExecutorService		-	The implementation of Executor, here is where the threads are created and managed\
\
Runnable 					-	The task that needs to be run,  							[ Note: This class comes from java.lang, does not return a result, no checked exceptions ]\
\
\
Callable					-	The task that needs to be run							[ Note: This class comes from java.util.concurrent, returns a result, throws Exception ]\
\
Future\
	FutureTask			-	The implementation of Future, allows to get the result of the task that was run in a thread\
